        "latex": "$(**)\\;2^{2x}-3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}=3^{x+\\frac{1}{2}}-2^{2x-1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((**)\\;2^{2x}-3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}=3^{x+\\frac{1}{2}}-2^{2x-1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "576b845c-1bc6-40cc-b48e-8b3016f44e4b",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $x\\in\\Rr$.\n\n$$\\begin{align*}\n2^{2x}-3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}=3^{x+\\frac{1}{2}}-2^{2x-1}&\\Leftrightarrow2^{2x}+2^{2x-1}=3^{x+\\frac{1}{2}}+3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow2^{2x-1}(2+1)=3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}(3+1)\\Leftrightarrow3\\times2^{2x-1}=4\\times3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow2^{2x-3}=3^{x-\\frac{3}{2}}\\Leftrightarrow(2x-3)\\ln2=\\left(x-\\frac{3}{2}\\right)\\ln3\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow x=\\frac{3\\ln2-\\frac{3}{2}\\ln3}{2\\ln2-\\ln3}\\Leftrightarrow x=\\frac{3}{2}.\n\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x\\in\\Rr\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n2^{2x}-3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}=3^{x+\\frac{1}{2}}-2^{2x-1}&amp;\\Leftrightarrow2^{2x}+2^{2x-1}=3^{x+\\frac{1}{2}}+3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}\\\\\n &amp;\\Leftrightarrow2^{2x-1}(2+1)=3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}(3+1)\\Leftrightarrow3\\times2^{2x-1}=4\\times3^{x-\\frac{1}{2}}\\\\\n &amp;\\Leftrightarrow2^{2x-3}=3^{x-\\frac{3}{2}}\\Leftrightarrow(2x-3)\\ln2=\\left(x-\\frac{3}{2}\\right)\\ln3\\\\\n &amp;\\Leftrightarrow x=\\frac{3\\ln2-\\frac{3}{2}\\ln3}{2\\ln2-\\ln3}\\Leftrightarrow x=\\frac{3}{2}.\n\\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
